name: dataTransformDatabase
usagePercentQuery
func:
var query = `SELECT
    COUNT(*) AS total_records,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_11) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_11,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_12) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_12,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_13) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_13,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_14) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_14,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_15) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_15,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_21) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_21,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_22) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_22,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_23) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_23,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_24) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_24,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_25) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_25,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_31) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_31,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_32) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_32,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_33) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_33,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_34) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_34,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_35) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_35,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_41) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_41,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_42) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_42,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_43) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_43,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_44) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_44,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_45) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_45,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_51) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_51,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_52) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_52,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_53) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_53,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_54) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_54,
    ROUND(SUM(pos_55) / COUNT(*) * 100, 2) AS percent_pos_55
FROM storagePosition;`;

msg.topic = query;
return msg;
